<div class="title">Rainy Day, Dream Away.....</div>
<div class="substance">Amanita muscaria, Blue Lotus & Alcohol (Wine)</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Vinz+Clortho&Exact=1">Vinz Clortho</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Vinz Clortho. "Rainy Day, Dream Away.....: An Experience with Amanita muscaria, Blue Lotus & Alcohol (Wine) (exp48106)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jan 10, 2007. erowid.org/exp/48106</div>

<br/>



